Ah, you're back, are ya, Guppy? [[Sell]]
[[Leave]] [[Why wouldn't I want the church to know what I've caught?|explain]]

passages.text: Aye, return when ya have something worthy of my coin.

passages.text:
Ya see, the fish the Church records informs the Choosing. And some folks want to make some coin without tipping the scales.
[[What is the Choosing anyway?|choosing]]
passages.name: explain

passages.text:
Stick around 'till tomorrow, Guppy, and you'll see for yourself.
